These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, papaya, zucchini, lettuce
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, malaysian, nigerian, german
1. the malaysian is on the left of the spanish##1
2. the person eating pear is the german##1
3. the nigerian is on the right of the spanish##1
4. the person eating papaya is on the left of the german##1
5. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lettuce | zucchini | papaya | pear   |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | spanish     | nigerian   | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, hiking, puzzles, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, baseball, ice-hockey, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | puzzles | magic-tricks | hiking | chess    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | baseball      | skiing | rugby |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, sudoku, board-games, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, western, horror
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | baking | skydiving | board-games   | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | western | horror | martial-arts         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, horror, superhero, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, baseball, climbing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is baseball is the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | horror | comedy  | superhero      |
| Sport         | baseball | snowboarding   | climbing | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, potato, broccoli, peas
4 different pets are kept: frog, goat, snake, chinchilla
1. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating lime##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
3. the person eating peas is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | peas | broccoli | potato | lime |
| Pet    | frog       | chinchilla | snake | goat     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, brazilian, argentine, italian
4 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, lizard, pony
1. the brazilian is on the far right##1
2. the italian is on the left of the argentine##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | italian | argentine | thai | brazilian |
| Pet           | snake      | lizard | pony | rabbit    |

