.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, rock, punk, funk
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog, bird, lizard
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the fan of funk is on the far right##1
3. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | rock | metal | funk  |
| Pet           | bird | guinea-pig | lizard       | dog |

