.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, videographer, social-worker, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, ship, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the videographer##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the pilot##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the software-developer##1
4. the social-worker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | social-worker | software-developer      | videographer | pilot |
| Transport   | motorbike          | roller | ship     | snowmobile    |

