The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, roller, quad-bike, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | animation       | comedy | epic   |
| Transport     | roller | quad-bike | bike   | trike |

