.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, 7up, mirinda
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, trike, subway, bike
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | juice | 7up  | soy-milk | mirinda |
| Transport   | bike | subway | trike          | airplane    |

