.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, juice, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, rock, folk
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of rock##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | juice | lemonade  | tea | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | rock | folk           | pop   |

