.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, japanese, italian, malaysian
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski, subway, quad-bike
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the pakistani is on the left of the italian##1
4. the malaysian is the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | italian | japanese | malaysian   |
| Transport     | subway  | ship    | jet-ski       | quad-bike |

 